ZH: 汽车的尾气对环境造成了污染。
EN: Car emissions pollute the environment.

ZH: 燃烧柴油会产生有害尾气。
EN: Burning diesel produces harmful exhaust emissions.

ZH: 工厂尾气是造成空气污染的主要原因之一。
EN: Factory exhaust emissions are one of the main causes of air pollution.

ZH: 为了减少尾气排放，我们应该鼓励使用清洁能源。
EN: To reduce exhaust emissions, we should encourage the use of clean energy.

ZH: 这辆卡车的尾气排放过高，需要进行维修。
EN: The exhaust emissions of this truck are too high and need to be repaired.

ZH: 机动车辆的尾气排放要符合国家标准。
EN: The exhaust emissions of motor vehicles must meet national standards.

ZH: 尾气排放对人类健康造成了严重影响。
EN: Exhaust emissions have a serious impact on human health.

ZH: 某些尾气中的化学物质可能导致呼吸道疾病。
EN: Certain chemicals in exhaust emissions may lead to respiratory diseases.

ZH: 飞机的尾气主要是水蒸气和二氧化碳。
EN: Airplane exhaust is mainly water vapor and carbon dioxide.

ZH: 柴油机尾气中含有的颗粒物对环境和健康都有害。
EN: The particulate matter in diesel exhaust is harmful to the environment and health.

ZH: 新技术可以帮助降低汽车尾气排放。
EN: New technologies can help reduce car exhaust emissions.

ZH: 政府应该出台更加严厉的法规来控制工厂尾气排放。
EN: The government should implement stricter regulations to control factory exhaust emissions.

ZH: 尾气净化器可以有效降低柴油车辆的尾气排放。
EN: Exhaust gas purifiers can effectively reduce the exhaust emissions of diesel vehicles.

ZH: 尾气排放会导致酸雨的形成。
EN: Exhaust emissions can lead to the formation of acid rain.

ZH: 在城市中，汽车尾气是主要的空气污染源。
EN: In cities, car exhaust emissions are a major source of air pollution.

ZH: 尾气处理系统可以将废气处理成无害物质。
EN: Exhaust treatment systems can process waste gas into harmless substances.

ZH: 通过控制尾气排放，我们可以改善环境质量。
EN: By controlling exhaust emissions, we can improve the quality of the environment.

ZH: 尾气排放量与汽车的运行状况有关。
EN: The amount of exhaust emissions is related to the condition of the car.

ZH: 某些城市限制高排放车辆进入市区以减少尾气污染。
EN: Some cities restrict high-emission vehicles from entering the urban area to reduce exhaust pollution.

ZH: 尾气排放标准的严格执行对环境保护至关重要。
EN: Strict enforcement of exhaust emission standards is essential for environmental protection.
